1063
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:20,630
A gaiola...

1064
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:24,840
...ou o reinado de Doflamingo?

1065
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,010
A fábrica...!

1066
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,360
A gaiola...

1067
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:38,180
Os fios...

1068
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,880
...desapareceram!

1069
